  "texts": [
    "In the input prompt, we integrate historical interaction sequences and reflections, prompting the LLM to generate appropriate thoughts for guiding subsequent actions.",
    "In these examples, we could find some interesting properties of the generated thoughts.",
    "In the case of thought example 1, we observe that LLM can analyze users' interests and decompose multiple rounds of recommendation tasks into distinct sub-plans.",
    "By leveraging its planning capabilities, the LLM can generate suggestions extending beyond immediate choices, considering their potential long-term impact on user satisfaction.",
    "This enables the method to take into account various factors to optimize user long-term engagement and satisfaction."
